<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The financial support granted under this Regulation to the projects chosen in accordance therewith may not exceed 25 % of the total cost of each project or of the particular stage of the project to be supported. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse alusel antav rahaline toetus vastavalt k&auml;esolevale m&auml;&auml;rusele valitud projektidele ei tohi &uuml;letada 25% iga projekti v&otilde;i projekti konkreetse toetatava etapi &uuml;ldmaksumusest. </eesti>
<inglise> Under no circumstances shall contributions from all Community sources exceed 50 % of the total cost of a given project. </inglise>
<eesti> Mingil juhul ei tohi maksed &uuml;henduse mis tahes vahenditest &uuml;letada 50% konkreetse projekti &uuml;ldmaksumusest. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> For the purpose of granting the Community financial support referred to in Articles 1 and 2, the Commission shall take the necessary steps for the application of this Regulation, in agreement with the Member States involved and taking into account the amounts estimated to be necessary. </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklites 1 ja 2 nimetatud &uuml;henduse rahalise toetuse andmiseks v&otilde;tab komisjon k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse kohaldamiseks vajalikud meetmed kokkuleppel asjaomaste liikmesriikidega ning v&otilde;ttes arvesse prognoositud vajalikke summasid. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> With regard to the projects referred to in section 1.3 of Article 2 (2), the Member States shall send draft projects to the Commission within 30 days of the entry into force of this Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 2 l&otilde;ikes 2 punktis 1.3 nimetatud projektidega seoses saadavad liikmesriigid projektitaotlused komisjonile 30 p&auml;eva jooksul alates k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse j&otilde;ustumisest. </eesti>
<inglise> Within 75 days, the Commission shall consult the Committee on Transport Infrastructures set up by Decision 78/174/EEC (1), take a decision and notify the Council thereof. </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjon konsulteerib 75 p&auml;eva jooksul otsusega 78/174/EM&Uuml; (1) moodustatud transpordi infrastruktuuri komiteega, teeb otsuse ja teatab sellest n&otilde;ukogule. </eesti>
<inglise> Within 30 days of this notification, any Member State may refer the matter to the Council. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga liikmesriik v&otilde;ib 30 p&auml;eva jooksul sellisest teatamisest komisjoni otsuse n&otilde;ukogule suunata. </eesti>
<inglise> The Council, acting on a qualified majority, may take a different decision within 45 days. </inglise>
<eesti> N&otilde;ukogu v&otilde;ib kvalifitseeritud h&auml;&auml;lteenamusega v&otilde;tta 45 p&auml;eva jooksul vastu teistsuguse otsuse. </eesti>
<inglise> If the matter is not referred to the Council by any Member State, or if the Council does not act within the above period of time, the decision of the Commission shall become final. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui &uuml;kski liikmesriik ei suuna asja n&otilde;ukogule v&otilde;i kui n&otilde;ukogu ei tegutse eespool nimetatud ajavahemiku jooksul, on komisjoni otsus l&otilde;plik. </eesti>
<inglise> The decision of the Commission or the Council shall be published in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjoni v&otilde;i n&otilde;ukogu otsus avaldatakse Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> On conclusion of the work which has received Community support, the Commission shall submit a report to the Council. </inglise>
